{# Llama-3-native system prompt for Meta's llama3.1:8b instruct model.
   Ollama wraps this content in <|start_header_id|>system<|end_header_id|>\n\n...<|eot_id|>
   per the model's chat template (confirmed via `ollama show llama3.1:8b --modelfile`).

   Llama 3.1 Instruct is trained with substantive system prompts that establish
   role and rules up front, then defer the concrete task payload to the user turn
   (see meta-llama/Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct model card and Meta's chat-template guide).
   Unlike Mistral's compact-system convention, Llama responds well when the system
   message lays out the structural constraints — the assistant has been RLHF'd to
